title: Egg And Sausage Casserole

directions: ["Preheat oven to 350\u00b0.", "Cut buttered bread into crouton size pieces.", "Stir eggs and milk together in a large bowl.", "Mix all the remaining ingredients in with milk and egg mixture.", "Pour into a buttered (or spray with Pam) 9 1/2 x 11-inch baking dish. Refrigerate overnight.", "Bake for 50 to 55 minutes at 350\u00b0."]
